name: Nina Ricci Eau de Perfume
description: Ricci Ricci Eau de Perfume arrives on the market in 2009, as a fragrance for glamorous and urban heroines. It is composed of rhubarb, bergamot, moonflower, Indian tuberose, centifolia rose, patchouli and sandalwood. Ricci Ricci was created by Aurelien Guichard and Jacques Huclier.
